Canonical website:
  http://alleg.sf.net/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/alleg/allegro-5.1.9.7z

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack allegro-5.1.9-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./allegro-5.1.9-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/allegro-5.1.9-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/allegro-5.1.9-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liballegro5.1-5.1.9-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liballegro-devel-5.1.9-X.tar.xz

